  "synopsis": "After passing out drunk on a cold night, I awake as a nameless young orphan girl. But she’s not just any girl, she’s a character from a novel I wrote in high school! Abused and sold at auction as a slave, I’m suddenly rescued by my father, Duke Henry Wensgrey, the story’s original villain. Far from the wicked character I created, he’s now a total fool for his daughter. But our relationship isn’t the only thing that’s changed, and I soon discover that this world isn’t anything like what I wrote! \n\n(Source: Tapas)",
